OL,3,CAsylum seekers could be housed in
OL,4,Ctraining camp in bid to end hotel use
OL,6,FUnder new government plans to end the
OL,7,Fuse of hotels to house migrants,
OL,8,Fhundreds of asylum seekers could be
OL,9,Fmoved to a military site in East
OL,10,FSussex.
OL,12,FThe Home Office confirmed on Monday
OL,13,Fthe Crowborough Training Camp will
OL,14,Ftemporarily house them, whilst the
OL,15,Fgovernment work to identify more sites
OL,16,Fin the coming weeks and months.
