OL,3,CAsylum seekers could be housed in
OL,4,Ctraining camp in bid to end hotel use
OL,6,FThe High Weald site was previously
OL,7,Fused to accommodate Afghan families
OL,8,Fwho were evacuated during the
OL,9,Fwithdrawal from Kabul in 2021, whilst
OL,10,Fthey were being resettled.
OL,12,FThe plans will also see men housed at
OL,13,FCameron Barracks in Inverness, in the
OL,14,FScottish Highlands.
OL,16,FOther options being considered include
OL,17,Fmilitary and industrial sites,
OL,18,Ftemporary facilities and disused
OL,19,Faccommodation, as officials accelerate
OL,20,Fwork to identify alternatives.
